data.description: Here it is! Beautiful, Your new Home boasts 4 Bedrooms, office could be 5th bedroom. 3.5 Baths, and a FULL, FINISHED, Walk-out basement! As you first make your way through the front door, you get greeted by a two story foyer with ample space, especially for your family and guests when you entertain! You will also notice that you can venture right off into your formal dining area or living room. Make your way towards the family room, just passing your den/office, into a cozy area to relax in front of the fireplace PERFECT after those long days of working from home! Your kitchen features an eat-in area, built-in desk,   large island, and more! Walk right out to your deck to take in those sunsets, and even venture down to your patio which is perfect for entertaining! All 4 bedrooms upstairs, and your beautiful master bedroom features an en-suite master bath as well. Beautiful views, 365 days a year, right outside your master bedroom windows! Last, but not least, head down to your full, finished, walk-out basement with full bath, kitchenette, Bar&Great room! Perfect to bring on those family parties, and can make your way out to the patio as well! Your new home is in close proximity to shopping, groceries, restaurants, the Fox River, highways, and so much more! Walking distance to the park, this right here is ready for you to make so many memories! Welcome Home! (newer items include: Hot water heater,Appliances,Freshly painted,All 4 tall long Kohler toilets,Sinks and Quartz counter tops). Some furniture available for purchase. Enjoy the common park area with you family with water views.
